<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/aug/05/">&#x27a0;</a> August 5, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="clear-air-travel-pass-data-sto" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://yro.slashdot.org/yro/08/08/05/1539231.shtml">&quot;Clear&quot; Air-Travel Pass Data Stolen From SFO</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I&#8217;ve always hated &#8220;Clear&#8221;, the pay-$100-to-skip-to-the-front-of-the-security-line card.  Firstly, because it&#8217;s private enterprise falsely dressed as security, and secondly because it creates a class system at the airport line. So my socialist side is smug to see the bourgeoisie get its comeuppance.  Have fun changing your biometrics, folks.</p>

