<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/jul/21/">&#x27a0;</a> July 21, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="ophcrack" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://ophcrack.sourceforge.net/">Ophcrack</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Windows password cracker.  Has an interesting open-source business model: The cracker is GPL, and there are free (but limited) Rainbow tables. To get the full tables, you need to pay $99.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
