<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/aug/14/">&#x27a0;</a> August 14, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="two-social-system-design-trend" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.brianoberkirch.com/2007/08/14/two-social-system-design-trends-that-should-really-really-stop-like-now/">Two Social System Design Trends That Should Really, Really Stop. Like now.</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;Yes, I know you’d love to have access to my address books and IM lists. But stop asking me for my login &amp; password.  Like to poke around my bank account while you’re at it?   Take my wife out for naked tequila shots?  How about just kicking me in the nuts a few times to show me who’s boss?&#8221;</p>

